    <item>
      <title>日本央行推迟削减债券购买规模，导致日元下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/boj-to-cut-bond-buying-in-normalization-step-as-rate-held-steady</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行要求投资者等到 7 月份会议后才能公布有关缩减债券购买规模的细节，这导致日元再度走软，并推迟了加息的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-14/boj-to-cut-bond-buying-in-normalization-step-as-rate-held-steady</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 14 Jun 2024 03:31:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市下滑，日元因日本央行债券决定而下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-yen-steady-ahead-of-boj-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本股市飙升之后，亚洲股市缩减了跌幅，而在日本央行决定推迟减少债券购买量之后，日元走弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-13/asian-stocks-set-to-fall-yen-steady-ahead-of-boj-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 13 Jun 2024 22:34:14 GMT</pubDate>
